{"tid":776144,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"洪永城浸佬味","createTime":"2018-08-11T18:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T05:20:56.000Z","uid":82917,"like":20,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3e57736678453db764fbfb185e3b87752231a9","tid":776144,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好想比洪仔仔無套中出屎眼<br />\n啊啊啊啊啊！！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n愈黎愈正，正到核爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015914_83b4d5799793b0f25f6f2b1ed75654d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015914_83b4d5799793b0f25f6f2b1ed75654d5.png&h=f7897a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想成為洪仔仔的老西，身上蘊存著他的餘香 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015915_83b4d5799793b0f25f6f2b1ed75654d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015915_83b4d5799793b0f25f6f2b1ed75654d5.png&h=1f9eeadf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n氣宇軒昂的洪仔仔，恍如光芒四射的巨星，人群中盡顯氣派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015916_0edcb72f977c527bde1a357702183562.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015916_0edcb72f977c527bde1a357702183562.png&h=e080c8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想成為洪仔仔手中的籃球，感受著汗水濤濕的掌心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015917_b6eabb517fcae8438d072a5887eed22c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015917_b6eabb517fcae8438d072a5887eed22c.png&h=677bdc12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n能有幸與洪合照，是何等榮幸！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015918_088cba47e0fa9d368f6e5629e21ea9bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015918_088cba47e0fa9d368f6e5629e21ea9bd.png&h=eaa87157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想成為洪仔仔的書包，羞澀地靠在他的肩膀上。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/015918_68f71faa88d42a5a0511440da0274603.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F015918_68f71faa88d42a5a0511440da0274603.png&h=3f28fee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小美已無法再用言語去表達對洪仔仔的愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">留在心底的愛慕～能否跟洪透露～ </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLove,<br />\nMay"},{"pid":"d0909d97892504a1b484e9c24c7802cc4d9ea14a","tid":776144,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:20:06.000Z","msg":"沒有人迷洪嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37eeec356545b9a08ddd933571269015a9630f5","tid":776144,"uid":196145,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:21:06.000Z","msg